data.description: Nestled within a prestigious community in Cumming, GA, this elegant residence offers a harmonious blend of comfort and luxury. Boasting 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this exquisitely updated home spans 2786 square feet, resting on a generous 0.26 acre lot. As you cross the threshold, be greeted by the allure of new flooring and freshly painted walls that weave a tale of modern elegance throughout the entire home. The main level unfolds to reveal a spacious living area, perfect for hosting gatherings, while the kitchen stands as a culinary haven, boasting modern appliances and ample storage. The bedroom on the main floor for elders offers versatility and comfort.  Each space is carefully designed to evoke a sense of tranquility and refinement. And there's more to this story Co a loft, a space that can be transformed into a whimsical kids' play area or a cozy retreat for relaxation. Outside, the property enjoys the seclusion of a cul-de-sac lot, with a fenced backyard offering a serene escape. Embraced by a neighborhood designed for families, a swimming pool and playground are just moments away, creating a delightful setting for all to relish.  Make this good deal greater by using our preferred lender Mortgage Atlanta and receive $2500 towards Buyer's Closing Cost. Ask Listing agent for details.
